    "body": "This has been discussed extensively in the past, and was a concious design decision. You can read more about the motivation on this issue (and associated PR): https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/issues/707. The short version is that not emitting those events makes it impossible to reconstruct the state from events only.\r\n\r\nIs this causing any issues in your application?",
